Title: Dead Air
Writer: Ysabelle Dean, Kerry Greenwood (novel), Mia Tolhurst
Actors: Essie Davis, Nathan Page, Hugo Johnstone-Burt, Ashleigh Cummings
Plot: When Phryne installs her new wireless she wasn't expecting to encounter murder on the airwaves and Dot realises her future is up in the air too. With Jack undercover it's up to Hugh, Dot and Phryne to solve the puzzle before more people die.
